Ask HN: What products have you bought for a different purpose than their primary
text:
Sometimes we buy products because we want to use them for something other than their primary purpose, have you ever done this, what was the product and how satisfied were you with the decision?

My product - The reMarkable 2 which I bought to use for reading ebooks because my kid broke my old Pocketbook - and which I have to say I regret because the screen is not light enough to read without using my glasses.
